title: LimeWire Pro 5.1.4 (MAC) - Includes Java fix for LW 5.0.11
description:
This is LimeWire Pro v5.1.4 for Mac. It requires a 64 bit Intel Mac running 10.5.


If you are experiencing problems with 5.0.11 or any other version that fails to run when launched, it was a bug cause by a recent Java update. version 5.1.4 fixes this and if you already have 5.0.11 installed, no uninstall is needed. Just mount the dmg and install and all will be fixed! :)


Please comment, seed and enjoy LimeWire.
